sections.heading: Sections; supplemental to other law
sections.text: Sections 79-1202 to 79-1230 shall be supplemental to any other law and shall not affect the reorganization of school districts as provided in the Reorganization of School Districts Act.SourceLaws 1965, c. 504, ยง 12, p. 1612;Laws 1991, LB 511, ยง 66;Laws 1992, LB 24
